msgid ""
"&rkward; was written by Thomas Friedrichsmeier and the &rkward; team. See "
"<ulink url=\"https://rkward.kde.org/\">the &rkward; website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; je napisal Thomas Friedrichsmeier in &rkward; ekipa. Oglejte si "
"<ulink url=\"https://rkward.kde.org/\">&rkward; spletno mesto</ulink>."

